            <sentence id="3.2">Steps to Reproduce:</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.3">1 Open Firefox</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.4">2 Go to Customize dialog</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.5">3 Uncheck "Use small icons"</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">Actual Results:  
The menubar grows in height due to the upper right icon</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="5">
            <sentence id="5.1">Expected Results:  
the menubar should stayed the way it was</sentence>
        </paragraph>
